title: Group Therapy: She's Worried About What Her Sister is Naming Her Kid
description: Emily called in for Group Therapy today, she's worried about her sister who's pregnant. Her sister wants to name her baby 'Drill' and Emily doesn't think that's a good idea and is not sure what to do about it.
